summary:
With over 5 years of experience, Renan has been developing his programming skills as a Software Engineer from an academic and professional perspective. Renan holds a bachelor's degree in Information systems and a master's degree in Informatics both from Universidade Federal da Paraiba in Brazil.

Renan has been working for companies across different industries ranging from start-ups to projects in the academic sector.
